{"tid":1839422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"醫護唔罷工, 等俾人做condom","createTime":"2020-01-24T11:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T05:45:11.000Z","uid":59976,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e29d8a18ed69119d0f5bc0c482fb757a486bd6f","tid":1839422,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"拋開道德枷鎖, 請罷工<br />\n唔罷既受害只會係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b734b77002154ba65d1eee5a737a98fd5fb10b2b","tid":1839422,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6a6LSdD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6a6LSdD.png&h=716f8927&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家政府決定中門大開，健康申報又不了<br />\n口罩又不了，港豬澳大橋仲要免費<br />\n大大隻字寫住wellcome to Hong Kong <br />\n你地日做夜做做到隻狗咁，又要搵命博<br />\n老老實實你地救得幾多個，政府一日唔鎖關<br />\n啲武漢狗日日落黎，周圍傳染你點救得哂<br />\n黑警就派9億幾人工，醫療削減開支<br />\n有圖你睇，啲武漢狗幾撚癲<br />\n啲病毒唔係源頭到減，香港唔鎖關<br />\n啲武漢狗就只會永無止境咁落黎<br />\n班高官就坐係屋企舒舒服服咁叫你去送死<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">懇請咁多位醫護諗真啲<br />\n究竟呢個政府仲值唔值得你去幫佢賣命</span>"},{"pid":"9fa5be86f329ba4e474bba991293b09b83c8ec9e","tid":1839422,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f37879f75aece9930aff2c8e66643f8077d483c","tid":1839422,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你唔罷工係唔會做到英雄, 只會變港共既condom</span>"}]}